OpenClaw Shield (Zig)
Copyright 2026 Contributors

This project is a derivative work based on openclaw-shield
by Knostic (https://knostic.ai/).

Original work:
  Repository: https://github.com/knostic/openclaw-shield
  Copyright:  2025 Knostic (https://knostic.ai/)
  License:    Apache License 2.0

The following components are derived from the original work:
  - 5-layer defense-in-depth architecture (L1-L5)
  - Secret detection patterns (15 patterns)
  - PII detection patterns (6 patterns)
  - Destructive command patterns
  - Sensitive file path patterns (18 patterns)
  - Plugin integration approach with OpenClaw hooks

Modifications and additions in this derivative work:
  - Complete rewrite from TypeScript to Zig
  - Custom pattern matching engine (no regex dependency)
  - Shannon entropy-based secret detection
  - International PII pattern support (UK, EU, CA, AU)
  - Skill trust analysis / static code scanning
  - Data flow taint tracking
  - Rate limiting for sensitive operations
  - Configurable policy engine
  - Structured audit logging
  - Multiple redaction strategies
  - Node N-API and WASM bridge targets
  - CLI binary for standalone use
